snippet.title: 👽Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures - Release Date Announcement!
snippet.description:
Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures is coming out on November 9th! 
Wishlist on the Meta Quest Store: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4859120967501314/

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1501820/

The release date for Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures has finally been announced! It has been three long years of work but soon you'll be able to play it.

Watch as you fly through trecherous environments, fight back against the evil empire, and utilise your small green friend to try and escape!

#metaquest2 #vr #indiegame #ue4 #ZCA
